"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"DAY6回歸前一日 數名成員出現不安症狀停止活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2010638/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2010638/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<br />\nDAY6 成員係TWITTER屌爆公司(JYP)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086346/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086346/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫個處於17歲發育期既女仔進行一日一餐減體重 被網民鬧爆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1919210/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1919210/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n強行進行演唱會 JYP宣佈TWICE首爾演唱會按原計劃進行！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1883747/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1883747/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nJYP不再續約(1) - 宥斌、惠林<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1847766/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1847766/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nJYP:拍拖OK 不過你開場萬人演唱會先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1808418/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1808418/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n白藝潾掰了JYP後首出輯橫掃榜單！ 「創韓樂史第一人紀錄」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1778449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1778449/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nJYP:TWICE的行程已經排到2021年(2019年11月)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1692072/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1692072/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nStray Kids成員的金宇珍因爲個人原因退出、解除專屬合約。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678991/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678991/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nJYP不再續約(2) - JYP留不住實力派歌手！2個月3人接連出走 網憂：只會做偶像？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1576197/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1576197/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n公司旗下相關新星預計大部分將離開JYP<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1278523/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1278523/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nJYP:父母相信我們把孩子交給我們，JYP放棄X101尹書彬<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/tJp38Cr.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lih.kg%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJp38Cr.jpg&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=4567ec35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/tJp38Cr.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1144211/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1144211/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nJYP不再續約(3) - JYP再度失去人氣女星！《三流之路》雪熙女神掰了JYP！ <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1121029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1121029/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nJYP不再續約(4) - 秀智睽違6年在台灣開騷，可惜票房未如理想。秀智與JYP合約將到期,不再續約<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1078219/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1078219/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n朴軫永因為TWICE新歌收到惡評「不要再給TWICE你的歌」「不要利用TWICE滿足你的貪婪」「我寧可聽到比較好的歌，而不是一直回歸」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/976087/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/976087/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n重談WONDER GIRL，朴軫永再遭網民鬧爆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1831069/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1831069/page/1?post=2</a>"},{"pid":"6397f72bced85fc759376a4bb4d20e8d00482e48","tid":2267424,"uid":28193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:13:47.000Z","msg":"咁大把職業都大壓力啦, 紅到既話搵大錢WOR, 運動員都慘架, 當你上到位, 三十幾歲都退休添, 你唱歌唱到五六十WOR"},{"pid":"c8c22f5515d90bd43c929be38969aa18ef7d12f7","tid":2267424,"uid":37146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n因為好早就出道17-20歲左右<br />\n係紅唔到都係24-26歲既事<br />\n出唔到道既早就轉行<br />\n其實24-26歲都可以做其他行業，只係慢起步啲，但經歷過練習生生活，一定更能克苦<br />\n<br />\n一旦咁好彩俾你紅到，真係人生贏家，錢多又後生，名利雙收，所以好多人都會搏一搏，搏唔到都係25歲左右"},{"pid":"86656dce5bb33fd94c2dddff47eb089ee3914dc2","tid":2267424,"uid":84104,"like":